      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm not talking about \"diversity\" or \"tapestry\" though. this wasn't just a feeling, it was a calling. i saw it clearly: the borders failing is a spiritual failing. if we don't stop this influx, the very soul of the country dies. there must be a higher law than just human politics. don't you think there's a religious basis for defending one's own land and people against those who would undo everything we've built?",
